

     
      Interesting and Important article for those developing applications in J2ME. This article is part-1 in the series of Reduce, Reuse and Recycle.    In this article, they have focused on performance and memory usage, as these are the two most common areas that developers experience problems.  The article explains the memory management in KVM and shows algorithm and code samples to deal effectively with objects.   The article has also shown the Tests that were performed and ends up with an optimistic conclusion.  [Category: Article,Level: Intermediate/Advanced,Java-Edition: J2ME]
     
    
